		"Name": "Amaris Fools: The Great Houses Must Fall!",
		"Details": "<b>ANOTHER ASSAULT BEGINS!</b>\r\n\r\n Terra, [[DM.Factions[faction_RimWorldsRepublic],Rim Worlds Republic]] Territory: Now that he has reclaimed his rightful throne on Terra and driven out the Blakists, the Usurper Stefan Amaris has set his eyes on the treacherous [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreGreatHouses],Great Houses]] who mocked the Periphery for centuries. He has issued a call to action, saying that the Great Houses must be felled out of revenge for the much-neglected Periphery. Interestingly, the [[DM.Factions[faction_TaurianConcordat],Taurian Concordat]], [[DM.Factions[faction_Marian],Marian Hegemony]], and [[DM.Factions[faction_MagistracyOfCanopus],Magistracy of Canopus]] have all openly agreed that the decadent Successor States deserve some comeuppance, though none of them have openly moved against the Great Houses.\r\n\r\n <b><color=#e51717>THIS EVENT CAN TAKE A SHORT WHILE TO PROCESS, DO NOT PANIC YOUR GAME IS NOT FROZEN</color></b>",
